 natasha pale and stern was sitting beside marya dmitrievna and her eyes glittering feverishly met pierre with a questioning look the moment he entered she did not smile or nod but only gazed fixedly at him and her look asked only one thing was he a friend or 
 like the others an enemy in regard to anatole as for pierre he evidently did not exist for her 
